\c 7
\s Ukwehlulela abanye
\p
\v 1 Lingehluleli\x + Luka 6.37,38,41,42.\x*, ukuze lingehlulelwa,
\v 2 ngoba lizakwahlulelwa ngokwehlulela elehlulela ngakho\x + Roma 2.1; 14.3,4,10,13. 1 Kor. 4.3,5. Jak. 4.11,12.\x*; langesilinganiso elilinganisa ngaso, lizalinganiselwa ngaso lani\x + Mark. 4.24.\x*.
\v 3 Kanti ukhangelelani ucezwana oluselihlweni lomfowenu, kodwa ungalunanzeleli ugodo olukwelakho ilihlo?
\v 4 Kumbe ungatsho njani kumfowenu \add ukuthi\add*: Kahle ngikhuphe ucezwana oluselihlweni lakho; khangela kanti ugodo luselihlweni lakho?
\v 5 Mzenzisi, qala ukhuphe ugodo elihlweni lakho, khona-ke uzabona kuhle ukukhupha ucezwana elihlweni lomfowenu\x + Zaga 18.17.\x*.
\p
\v 6 Linganiki izinja okungcwele; lingaphoseli \w amapharele\w** enu phambi kwezingulube, hlezi ziwanyathele ngenyawo zazo\x + 15.26. Jobe 4.6; 27.19,20.\x*, besezitshibilika ziliklebhule\x + 15.26. Jobe 4.6; 27.19,20.\x*.
\s Ukucela kuNkulunkulu; ukuphathana
\p
\v 7 Celani\x + Luka 11.9-13.\x*, lizaphiwa\x + 18.19; 21.22. Mark. 11.24. Joha. 14.13; 15.7,16; 16.23,24. Jak. 1.5,6; 5.16. 1 Joha. 3.22; 5.14,15.\x*; dingani, lizathola; qoqodani, lizavulelwa.
\v 8 Ngoba wonke ocelayo uyemukela\x + 2 Lan. 15.2.\x*, lodingayo uyathola\x + 2 Lan. 15.2.\x*, loqoqodayo uzavulelwa.
\v 9 Kumbe nguwuphi kini ongathi, nxa indodana yakhe icela isinkwa, ayinike ilitshe?
\v 10 Uba-ke icela inhlanzi, ayinike inyoka yini?
\v 11 Ngakho uba lina, elingababi, likwazi ukupha abantwana benu izipho ezinhle, uYihlo osemazulwini uzabapha kakhulu kangakanani izinto ezinhle abacela kuye\x + 6.21. 5.16,45,48; 6.9,14,26; 10.32,33; 12.50; 16.17; 18.10,14,19,35; 23.9.\x*?
\v 12 Ngakho konke elithanda ukuthi abantu bakwenze kini, kwenzeni lani ngokunjalo kubo\x + Luka 6.31.\x*; ngoba lokhu kungumlayo labaprofethi\x + 22.39,40.\x*.
\s Lokho okuqinisekileyo lalokho okungaqinisekanga
\p
\v 13 Ngenani ngesango elincinyane; ngoba isango likhulu, lendlela ibanzi eya ekubhujisweni, njalo banengi abangena ngalo\x + Luka 13.24.\x*;
\v 14 ngoba\f + \fk ngoba: \ft kumbe, \fq isango lincinyane njani\f* isango lincinyane, lendlela ilukhonjwana eya empilweni, njalo balutshwana abayitholayo.
\p
\v 15 Kodwa nanzelelani abaprofethi bamanga\x + Dute. 13.1-3. Jer. 14.14; 23.9,14-17,21,25. Mat. 24.4,5. Mark. 13.5,22. Luka 21.8. 2 Pet. 2.1-3. 1 Joha. 4.1.\x*, abeza kini bembathise okwezimvu, kodwa ngaphakathi bazimpisi eziphangayo\x + Hez. 22.27. Seb. 20.29,30.Mika 3.5.\x*.
\v 16 Lizabazi ngezithelo zabo; bayazikha yini izithelo zevini emeveni, kumbe imikhiwa ekhuleni oluhlabayo?
\v 17 Ngokunjalo sonke isihlahla esihle siyathela izithelo ezinhle; kodwa isihlahla esibi siyathela izithelo ezimbi;
\v 18 isihlahla esihle singethele izithelo ezimbi, lesihlahla esibi singethele izithelo ezinhle\x + 12.33. Luka 6.43,44. Jer. 11.19.\x*.
\v 19 Sonke isihlahla esingatheli isithelo esihle siyaganyulwa siphoselwe emlilweni\x + 3.10. Luka 3.9.\x*.
\v 20 Ngakho-ke lizabazi ngezithelo zabo\x + 12.33. Luka 6.43,44. Jer. 11.19.\x*.
\p
\v 21 Kakusibo bonke abatshoyo kimi \add ukuthi\add*: Nkosi, Nkosi, abazangena embusweni wamazulu\x + Luka 6.46.Hos.8.2. Mat. 25.11,12. Luka 13.25-27. Roma 2.13. Jak. 1.22.\x*; kodwa lowo oyenzayo intando kaBaba osemazulwini\x + 6.21. 5.16,45,48; 6.9,14,26; 10.32,33; 12.50; 16.17; 18.10,14,19,35; 23.9.\x*.
\v 22 Abanengi bazakuthi kimi ngalolosuku: Nkosi, Nkosi, kasiprofethanga yini ngelakho ibizo\x + Nani 24.3,4. Joha. 11.51. 1 Kor. 13.2.\x*, sakhupha amadimoni ngelakho ibizo, senza imisebenzi elamandla eminengi ngelakho ibizo\x + Seb. 19.13. Mark. 9.38. Luka 9.49.\x*?
\v 23 Njalo khona ngizakutsho obala kubo \add ukuthi\add*: Angizanga ngilazi; sukani kimi lina benzi bobubi\x + Hlab. 6.8. 2 Tim. 2.19.\x*.
\s Umfanekiso wezindlu ezimbili
\p
\v 24 Ngakho wonke owezwayo la amazwi ami njalo awenze\x + Luka 6.47-49.\x*, ngizamfananisa lendoda ehlakaniphileyo, eyakha indlu yayo phezu kwedwala\x + 25.2.\x*;
\v 25 laselisina izulu, kwasekufika impophoma, kwasekuvunguza imimoya, yayitshaya leyondlu; kodwa kayiwanga; ngoba yayisekelwe phezu kwedwala.
\v 26 Njalo wonke owezwayo la amazwi ami njalo angawenzi, uzafananiswa lendoda eyisithutha\x + 5.22.\x*, eyakha indlu yayo phezu kwetshebetshebe;
\v 27 laselisina izulu, kwasekufika impophoma, kwasekuvunguza imimoya yayitshaya leyondlu; yawa; kwaba kukhulu ukuwa kwayo\x + Luka 6.49.\x*.
\p
\v 28 Kwasekusithi uJesu eseqedile lawomazwi, amaxuku ababaza ngemfundiso yakhe\x + 13.54; 22.33. Mark. 1.22; 6.2. Luka 4.32.\x*;
\v 29 ngoba wabafundisa njengolamandla, njalo kungenjengababhali\x + Mark. 1.22. Luka 4.32. Joha. 7.46.\x*.